title: Contaminated fish from Communist China
description:
CNN Lou Dobbs report dated from June 28, 2007 about contaminated fish from Communist China.  The wonders of government managed trade with a Communist nation who is the crown jewel of the United Nations.

Our government claims that they are concerned with protecting American's lives from death and injury coming from "terrorists", yet seems to allow us to get sick and even die from "cheap" imports.

In the words of Thomas Jefferson, "I predict future happiness for Americans if they can prevent the government from wasting the labors of the people under the pretense of taking care of them".
